org.vedantatree.expressionoasis.types

Class Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vedantatree.expressionoasis.types.Type

  • public class Type
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the type for value object. Its default implementation is for java classes.

    June 2014
